      "description": {
         "value": "<p><em>requires attunement</em></p>\n<p>It also has the following additional properties. When one of these properties is used, it can't be used again until the next dawn.</p>\n<p><em>Pyroblast</em>. You may cast the pyroblast spell (while concentrating, the hammer increases in brightness).</p>\n<p><em>Immolation Aura</em>. You may cast the immolation aura spell (spell level 5). This does not require concentration, and continues until its full duration ends.</p>\n<p><em>Elemental Tongue</em>. You may cast the elemental tongue (Fire) at spell level 3.</p>\n<p>This can be created by obtaining the Eye of Sulfuras, a Sulfuron ingot, and the smithing plans that show the hammer‘s internal construction with the Sulfuron Hammer, and passing a DC 20 Intelligence check with smith‘s tools.</p>\n<p>You gain a +3 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon.</p>",
